Major Issues solved 
I work in all the environments like UAT, Preprod, Dev, Production.

Since all the platform is based on security, we have all the certificates installed from the endpoint applications which calls our api.
There was one issue where certificate was provided from  one of the applications but the app was still down, 

I checked and troubleshooted that one of the chain certificates were missing ,
We will have

Main
Intermediate 1
Intermediate 2
Root 

The intermediate 1 certificate was missing from their end, post installing all the certs it worked
